WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:02.133
I can't watch him fall apart

2
00:00:02.133 --> 00:00:05.266
I have handed over Huacan Group to Can

3
00:00:05.266 --> 00:00:08.466
The request is Can, not me.

4
00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:11.733
Can'er's father was wrong

5
00:00:11.733 --> 00:00:13.500
Please give dad a chance

6
00:00:13.933 --> 00:00:17.733
Dad knelt down for you, Dad, what are you doing?

7
00:00:17.733 --> 00:00:18.766
Kneeling knife

8
00:00:18.900 --> 00:00:21.133
Ouch, when I donated my bone marrow

9
00:00:21.133 --> 00:00:22.533
Liu Ru has already knelt down for me once

10
00:00:22.533 --> 00:00:23.900
Then I was trapped by ghosts

11
00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:25.466
It's not the bone marrow I donated

12
00:00:25.866 --> 00:00:28.466
And don't make yourself so dirty

13
00:00:28.466 --> 00:00:30.733
Even if your Jiang family is really down

14
00:00:30.733 --> 00:00:32.200
Don't you still have a good girl and a son?

15
00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:34.700
They can still support you

16
00:00:34.866 --> 00:00:36.200
Looking back, let's go

17
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:43.200
This Belle is just unreasonable

18
00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:45.666
You almost came down and begged him, and he still refused to save you

19
00:00:45.666 --> 00:00:47.433
Heart disease implicit heart medicine doctor

20
00:00:47.766 --> 00:00:49.466
We hurt him too much.

21
00:00:51.366 --> 00:00:53.200
You two go check it out

22
00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:53.966
5 years ago

23
00:00:53.966 --> 00:00:56.066
Xiao Can was kicked out of the house for stealing things

24
00:00:56.066 --> 00:00:58.366
There's also the matter of donating bone marrow to me

25
00:00:58.366 --> 00:00:59.600
Who donated it?

26
00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:01.233
Yes, yes!

27
00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:03.133
What that trash

28
00:01:03.133 --> 00:01:05.766
It turned out to be the future heir of Huacan Group

29
00:01:05.766 --> 00:01:07.700
Then wouldn't we be finished?

30
00:01:08.133 --> 00:01:10.266
What are you afraid of, no matter how powerful he is

31
00:01:10.266 --> 00:01:11.700
They are still the sons of the master

32
00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:13.966
I don't believe he can force me to death

